mg7dGjpJm2QyPowaKcyDP105RTDCb1oAB6fYLyHFNZ30H9RYBLU=
  "],ExpressionUUID->"f989745e-3d04-442b-a425-3ffa5d0b2d0c"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["A note on the sampling frequency and the Nyquist frequency", \
"Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9336973552167387`*^9, 
  3.933697397315762*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"74a84cc8-6f46-410c-97d3-\
429dbb4113e5"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The maximum frequency on a discrete grid of points is given by the sampling \
frequency\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["f", 
     RowBox[{"x", ",", " ", "max"}]], "=", 
    RowBox[{"1", "/", "\[CapitalDelta]x"}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"ea62659e-6979-4a97-999e-51505f92ddc8"],
 "\n\nThat is to say, the pixel frequency is the highest possible frequency. \
Note, that for an even number of grid points, the grids will run from\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"-", 
     FractionBox[
      SubscriptBox["f", 
       RowBox[{"x", ",", " ", "max"}]], "2"]}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"-", 
      FractionBox[
       SubscriptBox["f", "sampling"], "2"]}], "=", 
     RowBox[{"-", 
      SubscriptBox["f", "Nyquist"]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "fa72f066-26b8-41d1-99ca-ff619094972a"],
 "\n\nto\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     FractionBox[
      SubscriptBox["f", 
       RowBox[{"x", ",", " ", "max"}]], "2"], "-", 
     SubscriptBox["\[CapitalDelta]f", "x"]}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      FractionBox[
       SubscriptBox["f", "sampling"], "2"], "-", 
      SubscriptBox["\[CapitalDelta]f", "x"]}], "=", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["f", "Nyquist"], "-", 
      SubscriptBox["\[CapitalDelta]f", "x"]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"a7a31c1c-98b7-4ee4-8697-459d9d62506f"],
 "\n\nin steps of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[CapitalDelta]f", "x"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "02fe7f6a-89a2-4c7c-8507-5e0b62da942a"],
 ". In MatLab notation, we would write\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["f", "x"], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"-", 
      FractionBox[
       SubscriptBox["f", 
        RowBox[{"x", ",", " ", "max"}]], "2"]}], ":", 
     SubscriptBox["\[CapitalDelta]f", "x"], ":", 
     RowBox[{
      FractionBox[
       SubscriptBox["f", 
        RowBox[{"x", ",", " ", "max"}]], "2"], "-", 
      SubscriptBox["\[CapitalDelta]f", "x"]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"de3cdec0-fce7-4390-984c-f1c4bdad98fd"],
 "\n\nwhich is also,\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["f", "x"], "=", 
    RowBox[{"-", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["f", "Nyquist"], ":", 
      SubscriptBox["\[CapitalDelta]f", "x"], ":", 
      RowBox[{
       SubscriptBox["f", "Nyquist"], "-", 
       SubscriptBox["\[CapitalDelta]f", "x"]}]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"3563d863-6760-4541-b8ee-b526dc7f33e9"],
 "\n\nThen the frequency spacing is\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["\[CapitalDelta]f", "x"], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     FractionBox[
      SubscriptBox["f", 
       RowBox[{"x", ",", " ", "max"}]], "N"], "=", 
     FractionBox["1", 
      RowBox[{"N", " ", "\[CapitalDelta]x"}]]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"69c6778d-a293-4520-91b7-f10e27ef3e6c"]
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9336973677245827`*^9, {3.934034825442668*^9, 
   3.934034834799487*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0b6117bf-a475-4710-85b8-\
bc62ed63c50d"]
}, Closed]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Artificial Neural Network (ANN) Approach: Polynomials", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9336979163569117`*^9, 3.933697923296134*^9}, {
  3.9337029699910793`*^9, 3.933702979296034*^9}, {3.9337621979227457`*^9, 
  3.9337622002846413`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"fe4fe956-fdf2-45e9-92f6-\
6fced8fc720c"],

Cell["\<\
Artificial neural networks (ANN) are linear systems coupled with nonlinear \
activation functions. A general system diagram for a fully-connected, \
feed-forward neural network is shown here:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.933697934014063*^9, 3.933697976074027*^9}, {
  3.933698013092636*^9, 3.933698052914606*^9}, {3.93370296781266*^9, 
  3.933702968635028*^9}, {3.934034870229434*^9, 
  3.9340348734500113`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1654fbb2-d3cc-4109-a5d9-\
5def858e113f"],

