      "\n1. Exactly-Determined case\n     1a) function/fitted function\n     \
1b) bar graph with coefficients\n2. Over-Determined case\n     2a) \
function/fitted function\n     2b) bar graph with coefficients\n3. \
Under-Determined case\n     3a) function/fitted function\n     3b) bar graph \
with coefficients\n4. Non-polynomial case\n     4a) function/fitted function\n\
